column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, GN.distance, p.petroR5#_r, SM.logMass FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) AS GN ON p.objID = GN.objID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust AS SM ON p.specObjID = SM.specObjID WHERE s.z between # and # ORDER BY distance
